{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/install-love2d/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Wangoon Studio"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"ac8d4fc9-a6ad-5e24-bc4a-cf84cfe19704","excerpt":"Install Menggunakan ubuntu PPA. buka terminal favorit anda: jika sudah berhasil, cek versi love2d: Yay.. Love2d sudah berhasil di install. Tetapi Belum afdol…","html":"<p>Install Menggunakan ubuntu PPA. buka terminal favorit anda:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ruby\"><pre class=\"language-ruby\"><code class=\"language-ruby\">sudo add<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>apt<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>repository ppa<span class=\"token symbol\">:bartbes</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>love<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>stable\nsudo apt<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>get update\nsudo apt install love</code></pre></div>\n<p>jika sudah berhasil, cek versi love2d:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">➜ love --version\nLOVE 11.1 (Mysterious Mysteries)</code></pre></div>\n<p>Yay.. Love2d sudah berhasil di install. Tetapi Belum afdol kalo belum membuat game <code class=\"language-text\">hello world</code> :D. Buat file <code class=\"language-text\">main.lua</code>, misal didalam folder project kita <code class=\"language-text\">love_test</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">mkdir love_test\ntouch main.lua</code></pre></div>\n<p>edit main.lua dengan editor favorit anda:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"lua\"><pre class=\"language-lua\"><code class=\"language-lua\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> love<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">draw</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    love<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>graphics<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Hello World\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">400</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">300</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">end</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>cara menjalankan gamenya. masuk ke direktori love_test. jalankan perintah:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">zip -9 -r Test.love . \nlove Test.love</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5cc320a5cabfb4ab334f3cbc9fdcc797/ad00e/love2d-hello.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.08108108108109%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Love2d hello world\"\n        title=\"Love2d hello world\"\n        src=\"/static/5cc320a5cabfb4ab334f3cbc9fdcc797/fcda8/love2d-hello.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5cc320a5cabfb4ab334f3cbc9fdcc797/12f09/love2d-hello.png 148w,\n/static/5cc320a5cabfb4ab334f3cbc9fdcc797/e4a3f/love2d-hello.png 295w,\n/static/5cc320a5cabfb4ab334f3cbc9fdcc797/fcda8/love2d-hello.png 590w,\n/static/5cc320a5cabfb4ab334f3cbc9fdcc797/efc66/love2d-hello.png 885w,\n/static/5cc320a5cabfb4ab334f3cbc9fdcc797/c83ae/love2d-hello.png 1180w,\n/static/5cc320a5cabfb4ab334f3cbc9fdcc797/ad00e/love2d-hello.png 1366w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Install Love2d in Ubuntu 16.04","date":"February 26, 2019","description":"Hello World"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/install-love2d/","previous":null,"next":null}}}